{"tid":360304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記得有個同學成日著黑衫黑褲黑風褸出街","createTime":"2017-08-15T07:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T07:48:49.000Z","uid":137052,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01b86508a8027fc83830133a44770f9bd6b2a4bc","tid":360304,"uid":137052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:46:36.000Z","msg":"記得有個同學成日著黑衫黑褲黑風褸出街  <br />\n有次一班人上屋企做project <br />\n佢遲到所以幫手買lunch <br />\n叫左5-6碗米線仲有幾份小食   <br />\n等左半個鐘看更就打上黎問 係咪叫左外賣 <br />\n咁我地真係冇叫外賣嘛咪話冇  <br />\n然後就收到個同學打黎問做乜看更唔畀佢入 <br />\n先知佢畀人當左做外賣仔<br />\n最後打返落去叫看更同佢講頭先外賣嗰個係我朋友<br />\n<br />\n依家諗返起嗰陣一班人做野都幾warm<br />\n想約返佢地食飯 但個group沉晒底又冇人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0ed0fcb5acab3233d8dbacd1de60def31231fa","tid":360304,"uid":28515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://Facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFacebook.com&d=VmOzHJKbg%2FiC4ybfVgxIz10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=165bf451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Facebook.com</a>"}]}